platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: And just when we were getting the hang of surviving the wilderness, too Now were crafting boats, exploring tropical islands, and battling through the night. Klei and CAPY are a match made in heaven, and we cant believe we get to witness their Burton-esque nightmare.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Learn to survive in this world of both wonders and hidden dangers.
